---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import ContactForm from '../components/ContactForm.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Our story | Three generations | GK Swimming Pools"
  description="GK Swimming Pools began in the 1970s on a simple promise: work hard, be honest, earn trust. Read our three-generation story."
>

  <section class="hero hero--solid">
    <div class="container hero__inner">
      <span class="hero__eyebrow">Three Generations · One Standard</span>
      <h1>The Story of<br><em>GK Swimming Pools</em></h1>
      <p>A name that honors the man who started it all, our Grandfather. And the values he lived by, one pool at a time.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div style="max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto;">

        <p class="lead" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
          GK Pools: our name honors the man who started it all, our Grandfather.
        </p>

        <p style="color: var(--color-slate); line-height: 1.9; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
          When he first arrived in this country, he began cleaning pools to support his family. To him, it wasn't just a way to put food on the table. It was a way to serve his community. He led every job with two main philosophies: treat everyone with fairness, and take pride in every detail of your work.
        </p>

        <p style="color: var(--color-slate); line-height: 1.9; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
          In the 1970s, he immigrated to America with a simple promise to himself: work hard, be honest, and earn people's trust. He fulfilled that promise one pool at a time, building a reputation for dependable service across Los Angeles that neighbors still talk about today. To him, pool maintenance wasn't a transaction. It was a handshake. A commitment. Every pool he serviced reflected his values: fairness, integrity, and pride in a job done right.
        </p>

        <p style="color: var(--color-slate); line-height: 1.9; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
          He believed every customer deserved a pool they could truly enjoy, cared for with honesty and craftsmanship. That philosophy shaped who we are today.
        </p>

        <hr style="border: none; border-top: 2px solid var(--color-border); margin: 3rem 0;" />

        <p style="color: var(--color-slate); line-height: 1.9; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
          We carry that same mindset today. We understand that getting your business means you're trusting us to make sure your pool stays clean and running. Taking you on as a client is no small gesture, and we make sure we put 100% into every pool we work on.
        </p>

        <p style="color: var(--color-slate); line-height: 1.9; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
          At GK Pools, we carry his legacy forward with premium service, attention to detail, and a commitment to treating every homeowner like family. We don't just clean pools. We protect your investment, keep your water safe and sparkling, and give you the peace of mind to simply enjoy your backyard oasis.
        </p>

        <p style="color: var(--color-slate); line-height: 1.9; font-style: italic; font-size: 1.1rem;">
          From our family to yours, thank you for trusting us with your pool.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values -->
  <section class="section section--alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="eyebrow">What We Stand For</span>
        <h2>The Values We Carry Forward</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="why-grid">
        <div class="why-item">
          <div class="why-item__num" aria-hidden="true">01</div>
          <h3>Fair and Affordable</h3>
          <p>Transparent pricing, no hidden fees, no upsells you didn't ask for. You know what your pool needs, what it costs, and why, before we start.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-item">
          <div class="why-item__num" aria-hidden="true">02</div>
          <h3>Professional & Reliable Results</h3>
          <p>Every visit is documented. Every concern is flagged. Every pool is treated like it's our own, because that's what he taught us.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-item">
          <div class="why-item__num" aria-hidden="true">03</div>
          <h3>20+ Years Experience</h3>
          <p>Three generations of service and counting. The same neighborhoods, the same standard of care, the same handshake commitment.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="cta-band">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Ready to Work Together?</h2>
      <p>Let us show you what honest pool service looks like. Call us or fill out the form below.</p>
      <a href="tel:8188048204" class="btn btn--primary">(818) 804-8204</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <ContactForm />

</Layout>
